{"word":"ὁδοιπορέω","slug":"ὁδοιπορέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὁδοιπορέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὁδοιπόρος'><el>ὁδοιπόρος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to travel, walk</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ὁδ. τοὺς τόπους</el> <i>to walk over</i> this ground, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}